data.eml:eml: Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales "Bernardino Rivadavia" (MACN). Ichthyology National Collection (MACNIct)

Database of the collection of Ichthyology, contains around 6000 records and 99,000 specimens of the freshwater and marine fishes of Argentina, representing most families of the Argentine ichthyofauna.
